{
  "suite_name": "repo_intelligence_p6_llm_direct_success",
  "description": "P6 real LLM direct-success source suite. It requires LLM and patch-judge credentials through environment variables only, generates LLM patch candidates for a real GitHub repository, validates them through AST/scope safety gates and sandbox pytest, and records judge/sandbox agreement without letting the judge replace sandbox success.",
